        "calculation": "3 sizes x 3 variants x [(default,hover,focus) x (none,error,warning) + disabled x none + readonly x (none)] = 3x3x(9+1+1) = 3x3x11 = 99. Minus readonly x hover = 3x3x10 = 90. Adjusted: ~81 frames"
